    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely stunning vehicle in mint condition! It has been kept in pristine shape, looking and driving exactly like new. With its flawless exterior and meticulously cared-for interior, this car is a rare find for anyone seeking showroom quality and total peace of mind on the road.",
      "price": 48500.0,
